<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_open">
    <text>$player_name, this is $npc_name. Long-range ping from $current_level perimeter. Need a second pair of eyes on a route report.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_precond">
    <text>req_npc_rank:professional</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_timeout">
    <text>160</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_timeout_msg">
    <text>No reply. I am closing this channel and rerouting through another stalker.</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_1">
    <text>Send the route details. I will verify what I can from my side.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_1">
    <text>Copy. Three heat marks moved past an old checkpoint, then vanished near anomalies. Pick an approach.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_1">
    <text>none</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_cont_1">
    <text>2</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_2">
    <text>Info is expensive. Transfer payment first, then we talk.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_2">
    <text>Fair. Sending a partial transfer now for your time. Earn the rest by staying useful.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_2">
    <text>reward_money:1200,reward_rep:5</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_cont_2">
    <text>2</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_3">
    <text>Negative. I am not getting involved in your patrol problems.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_3">
    <text>Understood. Noted as refusal. Stay clear of that route anyway.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_3">
    <text>punish_rep:5</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_choice_4">
    <text>Before anything else, authenticate. Rank, unit role, and why you contacted me.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_reply_4">
    <text>Professional scout detail, independent loner net. Contacted you because your route overlaps mine on $current_level.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_outcome_4">
    <text>none</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_cont_4">
    <text>3</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_choice_1">
    <text>I will watch the checkpoint lane and report movement updates.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_reply_1">
    <text>Good discipline. If your report matches mine, I will share my reserve cache ping.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_outcome_1">
    <text>chance:45:reward_stash,reward_rep:8</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_choice_2">
    <text>If this is serious, I need hazard pay before I stay on that lane.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_reply_2">
    <text>Reasonable. Sending extra pay. Keep this channel open and do not drift.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_outcome_2">
    <text>reward_money:1800,reward_gw:20:stalker</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_choice_3">
    <text>I can dispatch supplies instead: anti-rads and med support by courier.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_reply_3">
    <text>That helps. I will receive the drop and update you once my side is stable.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_outcome_3">
    <text>courier_item:antirad,reward_rep:10</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_choice_4">
    <text>Too many unknowns. I am out.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_reply_4">
    <text>Then I reroute with weaker coverage. Bad call, but your choice.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t2_outcome_4">
    <text>punish_gw:15:stalker</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_choice_1">
    <text>Confirmed. Send your movement window and I will sync to it.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_reply_1">
    <text>Window is short. If this turns hot, I can call one loner to your flank.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_outcome_1">
    <text>none</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_cont_1">
    <text>4</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_choice_2">
    <text>Authentication accepted, but I am still not committing resources.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_reply_2">
    <text>Copy. Channel closed with no commitment logged.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_outcome_2">
    <text>none</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_choice_3">
    <text>Share collateral first: stash ping, then I commit.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_reply_3">
    <text>You drive a hard bargain. Sending one limited-use cache location now.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_outcome_3">
    <text>chance:60:reward_stash</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_cont_3">
    <text>4</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_choice_4">
    <text>I still think this is a trap. Prove me wrong immediately.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_reply_4">
    <text>Paranoia keeps people alive, but delay gets people killed. Your call.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t3_outcome_4">
    <text>chance:35:spawn_hostile:bandit:80</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_choice_1">
    <text>Call that flank support. I will hold until link-up.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_reply_1">
    <text>Support acknowledged. Loner moving to your signal now. Keep comms concise.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_outcome_1">
    <text>spawn_companion:stalker:45,reward_rep:12</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_choice_2">
    <text>No support needed. Just forward the final route warning.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_reply_2">
    <text>Final note: avoid open ground this $time_of_day. Signal drift is masking movement.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_outcome_2">
    <text>reward_rep:6</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_choice_3">
    <text>Understood. Send any med packet you can spare and close channel.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_reply_3">
    <text>Done. One field package queued through courier relay. Stay operational.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_outcome_3">
    <text>courier_item:medkit,reward_gw:10:stalker</text>
</string>

<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_choice_4">
    <text>This is too chaotic. I am dropping this contract now.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_reply_4">
    <text>Copy. Contract dropped. Next time decide faster.</text>
</string>
<string id="st_pda_ic_friendly_loner_1_t4_outcome_4">
    <text>punish_rep:8,punish_gw:20:stalker</text>
</string>

